{"TopicId":157731,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Are there hotkeys for RCS (prograde, normal etc)","CreatedByName":"michanst","CreatedById":172931,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-15T06:05:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"michanst","CreatedById":172931,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-15T06:05:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI looked at the settings and wiki. There\u0027s no hotkey for prograde, normal, radial in etc. I prefer pushing the keys than using the mouse to click.\u00A0Was hoping a mod that configures it. Link\u00A0please if possible.\u00A0Thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-15T06:13:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Key_bindings\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Key_bindings\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ctable style=\u0022font-size:14px;margin:1em 0px;background-color:rgb(249,249,249);border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);border-collapse:collapse;color:#000000;font-family:sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr style=\u0022background-color:rgb(204,255,204);\u0022\u003E\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\nH\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E thrust translate forward\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n0.11.0\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr style=\u0022background-color:rgb(204,255,204);\u0022\u003E\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\nN\